quote> 在香港，餐館供應生吃淡水魚是違法的，香港雖然是一個中國城市，但有自己的法律。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n外國人會唔會覺得好奇怪<br />\n即使係首都都唔會自外於整個國家有自己的法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd9773dd013dcbf4c27ca7d9c4e5fbea8211150","tid":782938,"uid":65815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ff1aeebebce6c0cec7fb9bf720edbd289537d80d","tid":782938,"uid":155088,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8b2fbacbbfdb5f57c7939d792653339ea5c812a2","tid":782938,"uid":162268,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"三文窮閪先食<br />\n日本唔食三文魚係有先見之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"日本仔就算食都係燒熟先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"三文魚唔會食日本人"},{"pid":"1bb283041bbac3256ead832a2b21347148795b61","tid":782938,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:44:23.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得三文魚好垃圾,食放題都唔會嗌"},{"pid":"102728f881bf9eef265bef1157d8c367f2a5426e","tid":782938,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"kelvin kwok 叫凱文 郭 咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428e9e062dda3edeeb50f287d0f0272411111512","tid":782938,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kevin kwok 叫凱文 郭 咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1046ed57626325a2518e06b1528dacdaecbb4dcd","tid":782938,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"大鑊，食開虹鱒既蝗蟲突然話唔食 虹鱒要食三文魚"},{"pid":"379b8fcb6f88fe40ac369ec8eb0aaa0a20dc27cf","tid":782938,"uid":72195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得三文魚壽司真係幾好食，但係近幾年愈黎愈多依d新聞，開始唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒無事先食一兩舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a23769cab0bba80cb90a9198500312c1e31d090","tid":782938,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"凱文&middot;郭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439d428531e36092bf152707db948210a7a2eb5a","tid":782938,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"劣幣驅逐良幣又一例子"},{"pid":"dd314e0a356e54d744b990f856916389db733f0a","tid":782938,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428e9e062dda3edeeb50f287d0f0272411111512","tid":782938,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kevin kwok 叫凱文 郭 咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"中文版記者hea的玩法<br />\n人地叫郭永軒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/abct/en/staff/academic_staff/index.php?id=whkwok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fabct%2Fen%2Fstaff%2Facademic_staff%2Findex.php%3Fid%3Dwhkwok&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=247092e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/abct/en/staff/academic_staff/index.php?id=whkwok</a>"}]}